description.en: LULZ is a token in the spirit of cryptocurrency community "memeworthiness" that is intended for true decentralized use cases, as its full supply was minted and issued into circulation without presale, prior allocation, or VC funding. This rare type of release promotes decentralization adoption through community participation with limitless utility ideas, specifically fair governance for any smaller decentralized project that wishes to adopt a token devoid of pre-allocation influence.
